Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:54.81,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}If I spend more time alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:59.23,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I thought I would get used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:05.35,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I'm a coward with a a straight face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:10.17,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,223)\be2}But in reality I was afraid inside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:14.99,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}It shouldn't have been like this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:20.40,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Only excuses keep piling up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:26.73,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I will be forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:30.78,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}From your memory someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:39.46,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}For a few more decades let's go for a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:43.99,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}To collect the things that have been dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:49.11,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}No matter what my future is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:52.44,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}But I'm not going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:57.79,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}To stop my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:03.78,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Someday I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.28,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Meet you again
